---------------Session Management-------------------


  Examples of session management:-
  -online shopping
  -userid password
  -chatting

http - stateless protocol


==Ways to have session mangement==
HttpSession
Cookie
URL rewriting
hidden form


==Way to create Http Session==
HttpSession=request.getSession(true);
HttpSession=request.getSession(false);
HttpSession=request.getSession();


==Cookie==
request.setAttribute
context.setAttribute
session.setAttribute


* context same for all the browser and donot change if request send and recieved is changed to null.
* request changes on basis of request send and recieved.
* session changes on each browser and donot change if request send and recieved is changed to null, but changes in other browser.
